With a letter Nidil Cgil has listed to the company the reasons that make the continuation of work problematic. Among the requests, the increase > of the bonus slot at 1 euro and 60, abolish the possibility of delivery to the floor, the visible tip also for the same workers and not only for the company, the double orders paid as two orders > and not as almost unique order, the abolition of the triple order, maximum waiting time > to the local for the order lowered to five minutes and waiting time to the local paid 15 cents per minute.
"The dissatisfaction of the Palermo riders - adds Brugnone - does the pair with the strike to obscurity of the riders of the same company that operate on the territory of Carini and goes to join the two disputes, thus coming to outline a single collective dispute". &nbsp;

